Package: daedalus
Title: Model health, social, and economic costs of a pandemic using
    _DAEDALUS_
Version: 0.0.8
Authors@R: c(
    person("Pratik", "Gupte", , "p.gupte24@imperial.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5294-7819")),
    person("Imperial College of Science, Technology and Medicine", role = "cph")
  )
Description: Model the health, social, and economic costs of directly
    transmitted respiratory virus pandemics, under different scenarios of
    preparedness and reactive interventions, using the _DAEDALUS_
    integrated health-economics model adapted from Haw et al. (2022)
    <doi.org/10.1038/s43588-022-00233-0>.
